---
// Starbloom Consulting LLC — Privacy Policy
// Edge AI & Automation Orchestration Platform
// No data collection, no tracking, local processing only.

import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Starbloom Consulting LLC Privacy Policy. We do not collect, store, or process personal data. Our platform runs locally on client-owned hardware with zero cloud dependency."
  canonicalURL={`${Astro.site}/privacy`}
>

  <section class="container-site py-20" aria-labelledby="privacy-heading">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-invert prose-slate">
      <h1 id="privacy-heading" class="text-4xl font-black text-white-pure tracking-tight">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mt-2">Effective Date: January 1, 2025</p>

      <h2>1. Our Privacy Commitment</h2>
      <p>
        Starbloom Consulting LLC ("Starbloom," "we," "us," or "our") operates an Edge AI &amp;
        Automation Orchestration Platform. We are committed to data sovereignty and operational
        privacy. This policy explains how we handle information across our website and platform.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Information We Do Not Collect</h2>
      <p>
        Our public website (<code>starbloomconsulting.com</code>) does not collect, store, or
        process personal data. Specifically:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>No cookies.</strong> We do not set tracking cookies, analytics cookies, or
        session cookies on visitor browsers.</li>
        <li><strong>No analytics.</strong> We do not use Google Analytics, Facebook Pixel, or any
        third-party tracking service.</li>
        <li><strong>No server logs.</strong> Our hosting platform may generate standard access logs
        for operational purposes, but we do not store, parse, or mine them.</li>
        <li><strong>No forms.</strong> Our contact page provides a beta application form. Submissions
        are routed directly to our internal systems and are not stored on public infrastructure.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. Platform Deployments — Client Hardware</h2>
      <p>
        The Starbloom Edge AI Platform is deployed on client-owned hardware. All automation
        workflows, AI models, and data pipelines execute locally on the client's physical machines.
        Starbloom does not receive, access, or proxy client operational data through our
        infrastructure. Data never leaves the client's premises unless the client explicitly
        configures an outbound integration (e.g., Google BigQuery, Twilio) under their own
        credentials.
      </p>

      <h2>4. Contact Form Submissions</h2>
      <p>
        When you submit the beta application form on our contact page, the information you provide
        (name, email, business description, and any attached message) is transmitted via an
        encrypted outbound webhook to our internal workflow automation system. This data is used
        solely to evaluate your fit for the Private Beta Cohort and to contact you regarding
        deployment availability. We do not sell, share, or distribute contact form data to any
        third party.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        Our platform may integrate with third-party services at the client's direction (Twilio for
        SMS, Vapi or Retell for voice, Google BigQuery, etc.). Each third-party service operates
        under its own privacy policy and terms. Clients are responsible for reviewing and accepting
        those terms. Starbloom does not intermediate or store data passing through these
        integrations.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        Our services are not directed at individuals under the age of 18. We do not knowingly
        collect information from children.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page
        with an updated effective date. Continued use of the website after changes constitutes
        acceptance.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For questions about this privacy policy, contact us at:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:fletcher@starbloomconsulting.com">fletcher@starbloomconsulting.com</a></li>
        <li>Website: <a href="https://starbloomconsulting.com">starbloomconsulting.com</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
